name: Zebra Mobile
overview: ZebraMobile specializes in helping newspapers develop and deploy a successful mobile strategy. JustForMe mobile content platform has been selected by many of the biggest brands in the newspaper business. ZebraMobile has been an excellent partner helping establish and build out the mobile presence in the Philadelphia market. With the launch of PhillyMobile on Philly.com, powered by Zebra, they have experienced significant growth in views, visits and in subscribers to the numerous mobile products that they now offer.
